title: Renegade 14-Gauge Closed Back Square Point Shovel with 47 in. Ash Wood Handle
description: After 35 years, Hisco's mission continues to focus on providing our customers the highest quality professional grade hand tools. The Renegade 14-Gauge Closed Back Square Point Shovel is a strong and sturdy tool that features a 47 in. wood handle. The blade is extremely tough and can withstand many years of use on the farm or jobsite.
